Create a parent div consisting of 4 child divs in a single row using flexbox

parent.html
<div class="parent">
  <div class="child">Child 1</div>
  <div class="child">Child 2</div>
  <div class="child">Child 3</div>
  <div class="child">Child 4</div>
</div>

parent.css
.parent {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
}

.child {
  flex: 1;
  height: 100px;
  margin: 10px;
  background-color: #ddd;
}
